item.title: HELP! Dealtascape HELP!
item.dc:creator: @TheImpureOne TheImpureOne
item.description:
@TheImpureOne wrote:

To move npc’s go into the config file and find Autospawn.cfg and find your npc’s that you want to move and change the coord’s of them to where you want to put them. the coords are the second and third numbers, usually 4 digit’s long.

And for Objects, open client.java and search for public void NewObjects() { and find the objects you want to move and change the coords to where you want them to be.

makeGlobalObject(coordX, coordY, objectid, direction, type);
